campus$.$College is located at basar village.
hospital$.$It is near second gate. There is qualified doctors and nurses there in the college. They will provide 24 hours service for children and staff in college.
mess$.$There are three messes in college.Kmk,marvel and telangana.It will provide good food for students and staff also. 
garden$.$There is beautiful garden also in college premises.
classroom$.$In one class room there are 70 students.
ground$.$There is vast ground in the college to play all the sports.
hostel$.$There are totally 4 blocks for boys and girls. bh1,bh2 for boys and gh1,gh2 for girls. 
labs$.$All labs are there in the college including furniture,machines,laptops.
canteen$.$There is two canteens in the college. For girls and boys seperately.
